title: First Date CPR
description:
Written by Kristy Lopez-Bernal
Starring Langan Kingsley, Avery Monsen, Kelly Hudson, Jonathan Marballi, and Dan Hodapp

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, June 2nd, 2014.

Edited by Kerry O'Brien.
